):

1. *Rano* je već izlazio sunce. (The sun was already rising early.)
2. On je *razumeo* situaciju. (He understood the situation.)
3. Ona je *razgovarala* sa prijateljima. (She was talking to her friends.)
4. *Razlika* između njih je velika. (The difference between them is big.)
5. *Reka* je bila poplavljena. (The river was flooded.)
6. *Razvija* se nova tehnologija. (New technology is developing.)
7. On je *razmišljao* o ponudi. (He was thinking about the offer.)
8. *Rok* za ispunjenje zadatka je sutra. (The deadline for completing the task is tomorrow.)